name: Trigate Wizard
desc:
Link Arrows: [🡱] [🡰] [🡲]

2+ monsters, except Tokens
This card gains these effects depending on the number of monsters co-linked with it.
● 1 or more: If a monster co-linked with this card battles an opponent's monster, any battle damage it inflicts to your opponent is doubled.
● 2 or more: Once per turn: You can target 1 card on the field; banish it.
● 3: Once per turn, when a card or effect is activated (Quick Effect): You can negate the activation, and if you do, banish that card.
